  Destrctor smiled as she washed her face in the sink. He new the replicators 
could wait for a short while. He actualy had not even eaten since he arrived 
on earth. He politly agreed with her and asked her to show the way. 

  There was something about this fembot that got to him. He could not put his 
finger on it. But he knew it was there. He liked the feeling. And hoped it 
would never leave.
